<L>__{exterior motel six parking lot night}
<A>__{pouring rain. as bitsey and zack hurry toward their rooms, they see belyeu getting out of his cadillac. he carries bitsey's umbrella and opens his own.}
<C>__{bitsey}
<D>__{belyeu!}
<A>__{he turns, comes toward them. bitsey holds a newspaper over her head, zack slouches.}
