<D>__{i employ mr. wright from time to time.}
<C>__{bitsey}
<D>__{you could have said something.}
<C>__{belyeu}
<P>__{(opening her umbrella)}
<D>__{that would have defeated the purpose. apologies if i caused you unnecessary anxiety, but i'm paid to be suspicious.}
